{"tid":109263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"魯芬bb R.I.P","createTime":"2017-02-05T23:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T23:19:27.000Z","uid":60403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa545495eedcb882c8a99fa4644ee87b60abf80","tid":109263,"uid":60403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T23:19:27.000Z","msg":"本月2日，突傳63歲魯芬因皮肌炎，免疫系出問題致留院，還需插喉，甚至已認不得人。同日魯芬致電回覆本報報平安稱：「多謝，有心。身體健康！」又稱現時「暫時情況OK，多謝關心。」並謂對於好友關心表示感激，笑稱：「哈哈，好有愛啊，感恩！」<br />\n<br />\n豈料事隔不足一周，突傳魯芬病逝消息，令人惋惜。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨3時許，魯芬家人發聲明，證實魯芬死訊。全文如下:<br />\n<br />\n「魯芬BB因皮肌炎導致肺部衰竭，於今日凌晨時分在家人朋友陪同下安詳離世，終年63歲。<br />\n<br />\n魯芬BB於十個月前患上皮肌炎，從得知自己患病後，她都一直勇敢面對，對戰勝病魔充滿積極樂觀態度。<br />\n<br />\n感恩各界的愛與關懷，適時公布喪禮安排。<br />\n<br />\n願魯芬BB早往佛國淨土。喃嘸阿彌陀佛！<br />\n<br />\n魯芬BB的家人字6/2/2017」<br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170206&amp;guid=56266639&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170206%26guid%3D56266639%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7222b4af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170206%26guid%3D56266639%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=4a322c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170206&amp;guid=56266639&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a>"}]}